### 1. GET courses filtered by department and semester
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/University/Courses?$filter=departmentCode eq 'CS' and semester eq 1

### 2. GET students with CGPA above 8.0
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/University/Students?$filter=cgpa gt 8.0

### 3. POST new student enrollment
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/University/Enrollments
Content-Type: application/json

{
   "studentId": "S100",
   "courseCode": "CS101",
   "enrollmentDate": "2026-05-31",
   "status": "Enrolled"
}

### 4. GET all enrollments for a specific student
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/University/Enrollments?$filter=studentId eq 'S100'

### 5. Filter courses where seats are available
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/University/Courses?$filter=currentEnrolled lt maxStudents

### 6. PATCH enrollment to add grade
PATCH http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/University/Enrollments(studentId='S100',courseCode='CS101')
Content-Type: application/json

{
   "grade": "B",
   "gradePoints": 8.0
}